<https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/133000205/2025-26/RA55> a ns1:LearningResult ;
    ns1:learningResultCode "RA55" ;
    ns1:learningResultDescription "Describir tecnologías de reciclaje patentadas: uso, potencial, etc. / To describe patented technologies: use, potential, etc."@es .

